sec.p:
All statistical analyses were completed on R Statistical Software (Version 1.4.1717) using the netmeta package.3,36 For direct comparisons, pairwise meta-analyses were conducted to estimate pooled mean differences and 95% CIs for WOMAC–Total outcomes. For VAS, we calculated the standardized mean differences because of heterogeneity in scale formats across studies. For example, some studies used a 0 to 10 scale (eg, Di Sante et al
16
), while others used a 0 to 100 scale (eg, Rezende et al
38
).
